Package com.library.frontend.controllers.operator

Class ResumeShowController

java.lang.Object
com.library.frontend.controllers.operator.ResumeShowController
All Implemented Interfaces:
Controller, javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ResumeShowController extends Object implements Controller
Controller class for displaying the resume content in a separate window. This controller is responsible for initializing and handling the UI elements of the resume display window.
